cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.CY, cs.CL, cs.SI 

The paper discusses the topic of explainable artificial intelligence, which is primarily related to the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). However, it also draws on research from cognitive psychology/science (cs.HC), social psychology (cs.CY), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and social informatics (cs.SI) to inform its arguments. Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
